Dialogue: 5,0:00:07.34,0:00:13.78,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,Humans pray to beings they cannot see \Nor whose existence they cannot prove.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:13.78,0:00:17.42,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,God, Buddha, or even mysterious \Nforces from outer space.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:17.42,0:00:21.49,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,If one's prayers are answered, they believe \Nin the existence of their guiding force.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:21.49,0:00:24.67,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,If not, they doubt whether \Ntheir prayers were sufficient.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:26.50,0:00:29.92,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, they continue to believe.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:32.95,0:00:37.64,Default,San,0000,0000,0000,,Please, let Arashiyama and I \Nbecome closer this summer. {timing check this scene}
Dialogue: 5,0:00:38.18,0:00:40.05,Default,San,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mean "closer" in \Nan impure way, though.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:40.05,0:00:42.82,Default,San,0000,0000,0000,,But if I had to say one way or the other,
Dialogue: 5,0:00:42.82,0:00:48.33,Default,San,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't be against the idea, \NI just wanna take it slow.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:48.33,0:00:52.65,Default,San,0000,0000,0000,,Something like that.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:52.65,0:00:56.45,Default,San,0000,0000,0000,,No wait, I don't mean like a \N"just friends" type of thing-
Dialogue: 5,0:00:56.45,0:00:58.09,Default,San,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I'm totally serious-
Dialogue: 5,0:00:58.09,0:01:02.20,Default,San,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I honestly value her feelings too-
Dialogue: 5,0:01:02.20,0:01:06.46,Default,San,0000,0000,0000,,If I just meant that in naughty \Nway, that'd make me a creep-
Dialogue: 5,0:01:06.46,0:01:10.15,Default,San,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, that's not the \Npoint I'm trying to make.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:10.15,0:01:12.20,Default,San,0000,0000,0000,,Uhh, I kinda lost my train of thought,
Dialogue: 5,0:01:12.21,0:01:15.06,Default,San,0000,0000,0000,,but since you're a god, \NI'm sure you understand.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:15.06,0:01:16.70,Default,San,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I beg of you!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:23.44,0:01:25.50,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever beings they may be,
Dialogue: 5,0:01:26.52,0:01:29.02,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,the hard part isn't granting the wish, \Nbut first figuring out what the wish is.
