Dialogue: 5,0:02:59.52,0:03:01.40,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,We are being watched.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:01.77,0:03:04.41,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,For the next 9 minutes and 16 seconds.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:04.81,0:03:10.15,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Separate from the cage of your body and its \Nperception, and surpass the boundaries of common sense.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:10.15,0:03:13.79,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,For we shall now set foot \Ninto a world of mystery.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:13.79,0:03:16.55,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Guided towards a realm of \Nneither truth nor fiction.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:17.80,0:03:20.50,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to the Maruko Shopping District.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.63,0:03:32.56,Sign,TV; Bottom right,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\shad4\3c&H575757&\fnHGPSoeiPresenceEB\pos(1042,396)}Live Breaking News\N\N{\c&H000000&\3c&H1D07CA&\bord2.5}Mysterious Holes \N Found in Empty Lot!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:23.22,0:03:25.90,Default,Reporter,0000,0000,0000,,Can you see this, ladies and gentlemen?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:25.90,0:03:32.56,Default,Rep,0000,0000,0000,,Last night, several perfectly circular \Nholes were discovered in this empty lot.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:32.56,0:03:36.60,Default,Rep,0000,0000,0000,,An apartment complex was slated \Nfor construction on this lot,
Dialogue: 5,0:03:36.60,0:03:43.32,Default,Rep,0000,0000,0000,,but there appeared to be discord between the \Ndevelopers and local residents opposed to the construction.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:43.32,0:03:49.55,Default,Rep,0000,0000,0000,,We've also received reports that a young \Nwoman's scream was heard during the night.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:49.55,0:03:55.22,Default,Rep,0000,0000,0000,,Just who made these holes, \Nwhy, and how did they do it?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:55.22,0:03:57.57,Default,Rep,0000,0000,0000,,This phenomenon just keeps \Nbecoming more and more bizarre. {timing check}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:57.57,0:03:59.47,Default,Rep,0000,0000,0000,,That's all for now, reporting live on scene.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:59.47,0:04:02.90,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,That was Miss Suekane, reporting \Nfrom the scene of the crime.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:02.90,0:04:07.41,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,We have with us an expert on \Ndigging, Professor Majima. {wtf is an expert on digging?}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.80,0:04:14.19,Sign,TEXT (left of man),0000,0000,0000,,{\t(\fscy85\fscx85)\be1\blur3\3c&H5A5A5A&\move(272,575,309,559,0,8370)}Digging Authority \N Prof. Taichi Majima
Dialogue: 5,0:04:07.41,0:04:09.70,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Please share with us your expert opinion.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:09.70,0:04:14.18,Default,Prof,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Certainly. I've dug countless holes \Nof varying types over the years,{he’s a diglett}{lol}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:14.18,0:04:21.20,Default,Prof,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}but to dig holes of this size and in near-perfect \Ncircles, one would require large, sophisticated machinery.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:21.20,0:04:22.69,Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Something wrong, Hotori?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:22.69,0:04:24.95,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}No, nothing's wrong.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:24.95,0:04:27.73,Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}If you don't hurry up and eat, \Nyou'll be late for school again.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:33.29,0:04:35.35,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Finally! The day has come!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:35.35,0:04:36.75,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Did you watch the news this morning?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:39.21,0:04:41.69,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I'm asking you if you saw it or not!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:41.69,0:04:45.41,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Kon, you're very "orange" today.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:45.41,0:04:46.39,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Orange?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:46.39,0:04:48.93,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,It means the opposite of "blue". {lolwut}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:49.89,0:04:53.04,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, you've been "blue" all day.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:53.04,0:04:53.90,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,You on your period?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:53.90,0:04:55.31,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:58.84,0:05:03.43,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,You can tell I'm depressed, so how \Nabout a little more consideration?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:04.07,0:05:06.27,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the time for this!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:06.27,0:05:08.92,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,You live near that lot with \Nthe weird holes, don't you?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:08.92,0:05:11.45,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Where is it? C'mon, take me there.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:11.45,0:05:12.13,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:12.13,0:05:15.32,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,What's your deal? Don't you \Nnormally love stuff like this?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:16.54,0:05:18.16,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,I know I do.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:18.16,0:05:20.25,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,I always knew something like \Nthis would happen one day.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:20.55,0:05:23.55,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Like waking up with horns coming \Noutta my head or something.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:23.55,0:05:26.23,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,And today, something finally did!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:26.23,0:05:30.85,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,That report convinced me that I \Nwas meant to see that empty lot!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:30.85,0:05:33.79,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, show me!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:36.24,0:05:39.56,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Do you hate living a normal life THAT much?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:39.56,0:05:40.94,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,I do.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:45.99,0:05:46.95,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Jerkface!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:53.10,0:05:58.84,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t know what crawled up your ass, \Nbut you could at least tell me about it.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:00.37,0:06:01.65,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,If only to get it off your chest.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:08.20,0:06:09.39,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,We're friends, aren't we?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:11.90,0:06:13.64,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Kon!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:13.64,0:06:14.78,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Hotori?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:15.35,0:06:17.62,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take you to the empty lot!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:18.95,0:06:22.41,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause I'm the one who made those holes!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:22.41,0:06:23.49,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Whaaat!?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:25.94,0:06:30.16,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,You see, last night, I went to buy some \NKoala Ice Cream from the convenience store.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:30.16,0:06:34.08,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, they don't sell those \Nat the Green Mart by my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.20,0:06:34.08,Sign,CONTAINER,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0.3\c&H5744BE&\frx30\fry8\frz358.414\pos(776,254)}Koala Ice Cream
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.20,0:06:34.08,Sign,CONTAINER,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&H60578D&\fnBlokletters Balpen\pos(667,417)}strawberry
Dialogue: 5,0:06:34.08,0:06:35.33,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,What flavor did you get?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:35.33,0:06:35.99,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Strawberry.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:35.99,0:06:38.30,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! Vanilla's obviously the best! {lolno; chocolate is}{you’re all wrong, buttersotch is where it’s at.}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:38.30,0:06:39.99,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever, just listen to me!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:39.99,0:06:42.98,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,So anyway, I started back towards my house.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:42.98,0:06:43.95,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,With that stupid doofus grin.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:43.95,0:06:45.37,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Just shut up and listen!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:45.37,0:06:48.93,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,And that's when I came across \Nthe mysterious device.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:49.68,0:06:52.05,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? What the heck is this?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:52.05,0:06:53.61,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,A laser gun?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:53.61,0:06:56.64,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Awful heavy for a kid's toy.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:56.64,0:06:59.00,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,There's no trigger or muzzle either.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:59.00,0:07:01.52,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's a model from some movie.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:02.35,0:07:03.29,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Bang.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:46.07,0:07:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{missing line?}
Dialogue: 5,0:07:47.87,0:07:50.30,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Huh!? What!? {at 7:53-55, kinda hard to hear} {timing check}
Dialogue: 5,0:07:50.30,0:07:52.14,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You want this?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:52.14,0:07:54.58,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying you want me \Nto give this back, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:54.58,0:07:55.40,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,That must be it.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:55.40,0:07:56.58,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Can he understand me?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:58.04,0:08:02.58,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Here, you can have it back! You \Ncan even have my ice cream.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:02.58,0:08:06.99,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,It's the most delicious food \Non the entire planet, yup.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:06.99,0:08:11.89,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure if you'd like it, but \Nplease try some before it melt-
Dialogue: 5,0:08:13.38,0:08:15.39,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Oh crap, there's another!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:15.39,0:08:18.14,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Another one! A black one showed up!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:33.49,0:08:36.60,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, w-who s-should I give it t-to?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:36.60,0:08:39.15,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Can one of you just take the ice cream?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:39.15,0:08:42.32,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,No dice, huh? Guess not. Nope.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:45.85,0:08:46.97,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,It's armed!?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:56.55,0:08:58.67,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, I did it again.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:26.50,0:09:32.21,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,And so all that remained was me, \Nthe holes, and my ice cream.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:32.21,0:09:34.72,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so that's what happened, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:34.72,0:09:38.80,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,You actually believe such a ridiculous story?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:38.80,0:09:42.10,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Normally, I'd just \Nkick you good and hard.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:42.55,0:09:46.78,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Am I gonna be arrested \Nfor making those holes?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:53.19,0:09:55.50,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,What is that? A present for me or something?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:55.50,0:09:56.41,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Dream on.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:56.41,0:09:58.06,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,I found it yesterday.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:58.37,0:10:03.09,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the same material as \Nthat laser gun was made from.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:04.70,0:10:07.80,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Relax, this thing isn't dangerous.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:07.80,0:10:09.95,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Lemme see one of the chopsticks \Nyou were eating with.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:13.15,0:10:14.71,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,You mean this?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:14.71,0:10:16.01,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Check this out.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:17.52,0:10:20.36,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck are you doing!? \NMy mom's gonna kill me!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:20.36,0:10:23.00,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Relax, it'll be fine.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:23.00,0:10:27.35,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,No it won't! Please don't give \Nme more stuff to agonize over!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:27.80,0:10:28.59,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Watch this.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:35.78,0:10:37.27,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,No way! It's fixed!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:37.27,0:10:38.45,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,It's back to normal!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:38.45,0:10:42.16,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,This is the reason I \Nbelieve your crazy story.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.16,0:10:43.91,Sign,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs70\bord0\fnExpress\frx8\fry6\frz348.102\pos(324,433)\c&H0B174A&}Maruko Shopping District
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.16,0:10:43.91,Sign,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs70\bord0\fnExpress\frx8\fry6\frz348.102\pos(325,434)\c&H161D79&}Maruko {\c&H141B6C&}Shopping {\c&H111862&}District
Dialogue: 5,0:10:47.41,0:10:50.84,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,The very next day after I found \Nthis, I saw that news story.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:50.84,0:10:54.03,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I figured something \Nexciting was about to happen.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:54.03,0:10:56.29,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,I've finally broken free from my boring life!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:56.29,0:11:00.55,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm at the center of \Nthis bizarre phenomenon!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:00.55,0:11:04.66,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you're the one who actually \Ngot to have all the fun.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:04.66,0:11:08.25,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,I'm basically just tagging along.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:09.52,0:11:12.31,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well, that's good enough for me.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:17.32,0:11:19.70,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just glad that I can be a part of it.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:26.03,0:11:28.41,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, the holes are being repaired!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:29.94,0:11:36.25,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,If, perhaps, Hotori placed a tiny headstone \Nin the Maruko district's empty lot,
Dialogue: 5,0:11:36.25,0:11:38.56,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,it would be in memory of the departed alien.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:40.69,0:11:42.67,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Now everything's good as new.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:42.67,0:11:44.67,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Kon!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:44.67,0:11:47.00,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,All's well that ends well...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:08.12,0:12:12.61,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,This incident actually took place, \Nright in our very own backyard.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:12.61,0:12:17.49,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Whether you choose to believe \Nit or not is entirely up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.88,0:12:25.76,Episode Title,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,"Grandpa {\c&HF58409&}Smart-Ass{\r}" (From {\c&H07F3F1&}Vol. 3 {\r}Ch. 28)
Dialogue: 5,0:12:26.21,0:12:28.04,Default,Grandpa,0000,0000,0000,,That your account leger?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:28.04,0:12:30.81,Default,Gra,0000,0000,0000,,You sure aren't living the high life, are ya?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:30.81,0:12:34.00,Default,Gra,0000,0000,0000,,You've never been able to \Nmake it work, have you?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:34.00,0:12:36.73,Default,Gra,0000,0000,0000,,Before the 100 yen shop, you \Ntried running a liquor store.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:36.73,0:12:38.40,Default,Gra,0000,0000,0000,,And before that, you tried selling futons.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:41.62,0:12:42.90,Default,Gra,0000,0000,0000,,COMBS ARE FOR PEOPLE WITH HAIR!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:47.36,0:12:50.37,Default,Gra,0000,0000,0000,,Ignored again... figures.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:03.26,0:13:05.56,Default,Gra,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you can see me?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:07.84,0:13:09.35,Default,Gra,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take that as a "yes".
Dialogue: 5,0:13:10.33,0:13:12.70,Default,Gra,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to your tail, fella?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:13.38,0:13:18.65,Default,Gra,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t know where or how you \Nlost it, but it must've been rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.44,0:13:21.52,Zenji,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(641,607)}Zenji!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.69,0:13:24.32,Zenji,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\pos(892,541)}Zenji!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.61,0:13:24.32,Zenji,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\pos(406,627)}Speak to me!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:25.53,0:13:29.01,Default,Gra,0000,0000,0000,,Please, carry on my dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.45,0:13:29.70,Zenji,Gra,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2.5\pos(1143,474)}Zenji!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:29.81,0:13:33.04,Default,Gra,0000,0000,0000,,A place where everyone can relax and co-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.20,0:13:34.33,Zenji,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2.5\pos(1146,462)}What?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:34.40,0:13:35.68,Default,Gra,0000,0000,0000,,Comoony.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.33,0:13:36.46,Zenji,Gra,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2.5\pos(1145,412)}Cocoa? {??? = cocoa brown}
Dialogue: 5,0:13:36.45,0:13:38.14,Default,Gra,0000,0000,0000,,Comyunee.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.33,0:13:38.21,Zenji,Gra,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2.5\pos(1143,395)}Kelp?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:38.14,0:13:39.37,Default,Gra,0000,0000,0000,,Comyumee.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.08,0:13:40.96,Zenji,Gra,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2.5\pos(898,104)}Do you mean "communicate"?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:40.96,0:13:42.84,Default,Gra,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's it.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:04.52,0:14:05.88,Default,Gra,0000,0000,0000,,Am I dead?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:06.42,0:14:08.09,Default,Gra,0000,0000,0000,,I blew my last chance...
Dialogue: 5,0:14:08.09,0:14:11.87,Default,Gra,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't remember the word, \Nand never got to say it.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:11.87,0:14:16.50,Default,Gra,0000,0000,0000,,I was a stubborn fool ‘till the very end.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:16.50,0:14:20.50,Default,Gra,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't really have any regrets.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:32.39,0:14:34.23,Default,Gra,0000,0000,0000,,They've come to pick me up, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:39.75,0:14:40.49,Default,Gra,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:41.86,0:14:43.23,Default,Gra,0000,0000,0000,,Guess they weren't here for me.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:50.46,0:14:51.03,Default,Gra,0000,0000,0000,,Ah-
Dialogue: 5,0:15:07.00,0:15:09.00,Default,Gra,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where's MY escort!?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:10.88,0:15:18.25,Default,Gra,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know who caused that screw-up, but for \Nthe past 10 years I've been wandering here, all alone.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:18.25,0:15:19.26,Default,Gra,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty neat, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:19.66,0:15:22.02,Default,Gra,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we've both been through a lot.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:23.71,0:15:24.31,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Found you!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:24.31,0:15:25.02,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Coban!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:25.02,0:15:28.78,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you always running off on your own?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:28.78,0:15:30.22,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,You're fickleness incarnate.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:31.17,0:15:33.22,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,What are you staring at, anyway?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:34.78,0:15:37.70,Default,Gra,0000,0000,0000,,See ya. You hang in there, okay?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:37.70,0:15:39.79,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Are you following something?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:40.40,0:15:42.50,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're freakin' me out!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:42.50,0:15:44.80,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you see a ghost or something!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:44.80,0:15:46.69,Default,Gra,0000,0000,0000,,Well excuse me for being a ghost!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:49.92,0:15:53.43,Default,Gra,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, I do \Noften meet eyes with animals.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:01.23,0:16:04.60,Default,Gra,0000,0000,0000,,But not once have people ever noticed me.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:08.36,0:16:11.65,Default,Gra,0000,0000,0000,,Not even the priest notices me.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:15.43,0:16:17.33,Default,Tak,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, Josephine, run!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:18.05,0:16:20.06,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,She's hell-bent on just walking, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:20.06,0:16:23.00,Default,Tak,0000,0000,0000,,We're not gonna walk you if you're \Nnot getting anything out of it.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:23.00,0:16:23.76,Default,Gra,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:26.22,0:16:28.36,Default,Gra,0000,0000,0000,,Guess there's animals that are oblivious too.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:30.38,0:16:32.70,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,So? What about this girl, now?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:32.70,0:16:35.30,Default,Tak,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. She's something else, I tell ya.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:35.30,0:16:37.59,Default,Tak,0000,0000,0000,,How do I put it. It's almost like...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:37.61,0:16:38.60,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Like what?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:38.60,0:16:39.91,Default,Tak,0000,0000,0000,,A rock lobster!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:39.91,0:16:41.20,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of analogy is that!?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:41.40,0:16:43.30,Default,Gra,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, nice timing.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:44.51,0:16:46.64,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta work on your vocabulary.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:48.44,0:16:50.68,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Takeru, you got the hots for her?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:50.68,0:16:54.24,Default,Tak,0000,0000,0000,,I do not! You always have to bring that up!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:01.24,0:17:02.76,Default,Uki,0000,0000,0000,,There we go...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:09.21,0:17:13.55,Default,Uki,0000,0000,0000,,I thought of making deep-fried tofu today. {yum}
Dialogue: 5,0:17:13.55,0:17:19.12,Default,Uki,0000,0000,0000,,But apparently, Hotori wolfed \Nit down sometime yesterday. {no tofu for you, acf}
Dialogue: 5,0:17:20.29,0:17:22.85,Default,Uki,0000,0000,0000,,She's quite the handful, that girl.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:22.85,0:17:25.23,Default,Gra,0000,0000,0000,,No big deal. Old fashioned tofu is just fine.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:25.23,0:17:29.42,Default,Uki,0000,0000,0000,,The men from the shopping \Ndistrict were at it again, too.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:29.42,0:17:31.39,Default,Uki,0000,0000,0000,,They just won't pay attention \Nwhen I tell 'em to shut up.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:31.39,0:17:33.32,Default,Uki,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't they just argue \Nat their own stores?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:33.32,0:17:37.32,Default,Gra,0000,0000,0000,,They can't help it. Men just never grow up.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:37.32,0:17:41.58,Default,Uki,0000,0000,0000,,If you were still here, I bet you'd \Nbe in there making a fuss too.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:43.20,0:17:46.77,Default,Uki,0000,0000,0000,,Y'know, I think it's finally \Nstarting to get livelier again.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:47.35,0:17:49.30,Default,Uki,0000,0000,0000,,Just like when you were there.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:49.30,0:17:51.75,Default,Gra,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's been ten years already.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:51.75,0:17:55.76,Default,Gra,0000,0000,0000,,If you keep praying that hard, \NI'm gonna have to move on.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:59.96,0:18:01.80,Default,Uki,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, goodnight dear.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:02.76,0:18:06.51,Default,Uki,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... where'd I put it?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:06.51,0:18:11.11,Default,Uki,0000,0000,0000,,This'll work for today, right? You \Nalways loved bananas, didn't you?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:12.86,0:18:14.92,Default,Uki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:14.92,0:18:15.75,Default,Uki,0000,0000,0000,,I think so.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:15.75,0:18:19.12,Default,Gra,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you're not praying THAT hard...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:19.12,0:18:24.21,Default,Gra,0000,0000,0000,,Guess you're at the age where \Nyou start forgetting my habits.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:24.95,0:18:27.25,Default,Uki,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't forget a damn thing.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:27.25,0:18:28.14,Default,Gra,0000,0000,0000,,Ack!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:30.08,0:18:33.38,Default,Uki,0000,0000,0000,,You've never even bothered \Nto show up in my dreams.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:33.38,0:18:34.84,Default,Uki,0000,0000,0000,,Some husband you were.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:34.84,0:18:36.26,Default,Gra,0000,0000,0000,,How about right now!?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:36.26,0:18:39.88,Default,Uki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well, you're probably just \Ngoofing off on the other side.
