Dialogue: 5,0:18:53.33,0:18:55.29,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, cut the crap, man!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:55.29,0:18:57.62,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Kobuhei's my disciple!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:57.62,0:18:59.85,Default,Bald,0000,0000,0000,,You just don't get it, do you?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:59.85,0:19:02.19,Default,Bald,0000,0000,0000,,I SAID he's MY disciple!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:02.19,0:19:05.08,Default,Bald,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I made up that nickname anyway!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:05.08,0:19:07.56,Default,Gra,0000,0000,0000,,You're screwed no matter \Nwho you go with, huh pal?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:08.91,0:19:11.69,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you were late again today.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:11.69,0:19:17.02,Default,Tat,0000,0000,0000,,And you yawned during class even though you \Ncame late. No wonder the teacher got mad.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:17.02,0:19:22.18,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,But I thought he'd let it slide \Nsince the week just started.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:22.18,0:19:23.20,Default,Tat,0000,0000,0000,,Not a chance.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:23.20,0:19:23.64,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,I know...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:23.64,0:19:24.65,Default,San,0000,0000,0000,,Dream on.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:24.65,0:19:25.13,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,I know...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:25.13,0:19:26.09,Default,Gra,0000,0000,0000,,The hell he would.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:26.09,0:19:27.25,Default,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I get it...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:27.50,0:19:29.74,Default,San,0000,0000,0000,,You're seriously gonna be held back.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:29.74,0:19:31.34,Default,Tat,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening! {gonna catch shit for that one, lol}
Dialogue: 5,0:19:31.94,0:19:34.98,Default,Gra,0000,0000,0000,,There's lots of folks to \Nchat with up here, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:36.95,0:19:40.49,Default,Gra,0000,0000,0000,,Hey now, you're gonna get it \Nfrom that blonde lass again.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:53.89,0:19:54.75,Default,Uki,0000,0000,0000,,Toshiko.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:54.75,0:19:55.25,Default,Tat,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:55.53,0:19:59.27,Default,Uki,0000,0000,0000,,Would you please fix a cup of coffee \Nand leave it by the back booth?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:02.74,0:20:04.31,Default,Tat,0000,0000,0000,,You mean this one?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:04.31,0:20:05.74,Default,Uki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, thanks dear.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:18.72,0:20:19.59,Default,Gra,0000,0000,0000,,Uki...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:22.60,0:20:25.16,Default,Gra,0000,0000,0000,,You can see me?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:43.22,0:20:44.52,Default,Gra,0000,0000,0000,,THAT WAS FOR YOU!? {way to kill the mood, jeez}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:45.39,0:20:47.51,Default,Uki,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh. Good stuff.
