Dialogue: 5,0:20:54.53,0:21:00.89,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,Humans pray to beings they cannot see \Nor whose existence they cannot prove.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:00.89,0:21:04.30,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,If one's prayers are answered, they believe \Nin the existence of their guiding force.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:04.30,0:21:07.70,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,If not, they doubt whether \Ntheir prayers were sufficient. {timing check}
Dialogue: 5,0:21:09.52,0:21:12.97,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, they still choose to believe.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:15.92,0:21:20.68,Default,San,0000,0000,0000,,Please, let Arashiyama and I \Nbecome closer this summer. {Timing check this scene}
Dialogue: 5,0:21:20.68,0:21:25.84,Default,San,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mean "closer" in \Nan impure way, though.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:25.84,0:21:28.97,Default,San,0000,0000,0000,,But if I had to say one way or the other,
Dialogue: 5,0:21:28.97,0:21:33.22,Default,San,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't be against the idea, \NI just wanna take it slow.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:33.22,0:21:35.63,Default,San,0000,0000,0000,,Something like that.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:35.64,0:21:39.44,Default,San,0000,0000,0000,,No wait, I don't mean like a \N"just friends" type of thing-
Dialogue: 5,0:21:39.44,0:21:41.14,Default,San,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I'm totally serious-
Dialogue: 5,0:21:41.14,0:21:45.28,Default,San,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I honestly value her feelings too-
Dialogue: 5,0:21:45.29,0:21:49.49,Default,San,0000,0000,0000,,If I just meant that in naughty \Nway, that'd make me a creep-
Dialogue: 5,0:21:49.49,0:21:53.17,Default,San,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, that's not the \Npoint I'm trying to make.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:53.17,0:21:55.25,Default,San,0000,0000,0000,,Uhh, I kinda lost my train of thought,
Dialogue: 5,0:21:55.25,0:21:58.05,Default,San,0000,0000,0000,,but since you're a god, \NI'm sure you understand.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:58.05,0:21:59.78,Default,San,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I beg of you!
